text: The one thing we have in common with the Kardashian/Jenners (apart from our constant family rows), is a love of makeup. While we know they love a #spon Instagram post, the sisters have also shared their favourite products numerous times, without being paid. So, we did a deep dive of their social media and found Kim, Kylie, Khloe and Kourtney's genuine, favourite makeup products...
title: 13 makeup products the Kardashians actually use, and not because they're paid to
